message.text:
📣 APPLICATION PERIOD EXTENDED‼️⏳

Hindi pa ba kumpleto ang requirements mo o hindi ka pa nakakapagpasa ng application? Worry no more—dahil may good news kami para sa’yo! 

Extended na ang ating application period! May dagdag na oras ka na para ayusin, tapusin, at siguraduhing maipasa ang lahat ng iyong kailangan. 📑

Huwag nang hintayin ang huling araw—gamitin ang mga oras na ito para makumpleto ang iyong application at maging bahagi ng kwentong bubuuin natin ngayong taon.

Kilalanin pa ang FEU IABF Student Council S.Y. 2025–2026 divisions dito: https://bit.ly/IABF_SC_Division_Description_and_Requirements

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
Powerband: https://bit.ly/4gcoxgT
PDDC: https://bit.ly/46wHPcL

#FinestKwentoEveryKanto 
#SoaringGreaterHeights

message.text:
📚 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐮𝐜𝐤 𝐭𝐨 𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬!

As they take on the 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿-𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 this September 16, let us wish our brilliant representatives the best of luck:

• 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀, 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵
• 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮, 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴
• 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮, 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻
• 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼, 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲

Your hard work, dedication, and passion for learning have brought you this far, and we believe you have what it takes to truly excel and make us proud. This is your moment to showcase not just knowledge, but also the spirit of teamwork and perseverance that defines a true MedTech Tamaraw. 

Know that you carry the pride and full support of the entire FEU MT community. Goodluck, quizzers!

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Caption by Peachie Corinne Sulit
Publication Material by Rein Louisse Dela Cruz & JC Sadang

message.text:
📚 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐮𝐜𝐤 𝐭𝐨 𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬!

As they take on the 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿-𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 this September 16, let us wish our brilliant representatives the best of luck:

• 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀, 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵
• 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮, 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴
• 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮, 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻
• 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼, 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲

Your hard work, dedication, and passion for learning have brought you this far, and we believe you have what it takes to truly excel and make us proud. This is your moment to showcase not just knowledge, but also the spirit of teamwork and perseverance that defines a true MedTech Tamaraw. 

Know that you carry the pride and full support of the entire FEU MT community. Goodluck, quizzers!

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Caption by Peachie Corinne Sulit
Publication Material by Rein Louisse Dela Cruz & JC Sadang

message.text:
📚 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐮𝐜𝐤 𝐭𝐨 𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬!

As they take on the 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿-𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 this September 16, let us wish our brilliant representatives the best of luck:

• 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀, 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵
• 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮, 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴
• 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮, 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻
• 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼, 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲

Your hard work, dedication, and passion for learning have brought you this far, and we believe you have what it takes to truly excel and make us proud. This is your moment to showcase not just knowledge, but also the spirit of teamwork and perseverance that defines a true MedTech Tamaraw. 

Know that you carry the pride and full support of the entire FEU MT community. Goodluck, quizzers!

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Caption by Peachie Corinne Sulit
Publication Material by Rein Louisse Dela Cruz & JC Sadang

message.text:
📚 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐮𝐜𝐤 𝐭𝐨 𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬!

As they take on the 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿-𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 this September 16, let us wish our brilliant representatives the best of luck:

• 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀, 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵
• 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮, 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴
• 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮, 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻
• 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼, 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲

Your hard work, dedication, and passion for learning have brought you this far, and we believe you have what it takes to truly excel and make us proud. This is your moment to showcase not just knowledge, but also the spirit of teamwork and perseverance that defines a true MedTech Tamaraw. 

Know that you carry the pride and full support of the entire FEU MT community. Goodluck, quizzers!

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Caption by Peachie Corinne Sulit
Publication Material by Rein Louisse Dela Cruz & JC Sadang

message.text:
📚 𝐁𝐞𝐬𝐭 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐮𝐜𝐤 𝐭𝐨 𝐎𝐮𝐫 𝐐𝐮𝐢𝐳𝐳𝐞𝐫𝐬!

As they take on the 𝟰𝟰𝘁𝗵 𝗣𝗔𝗠𝗘𝗧-𝗣𝗔𝗦𝗠𝗘𝗧𝗛 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿-𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗤𝘂𝗶𝘇 𝗦𝗵𝗼𝘄 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 this September 16, let us wish our brilliant representatives the best of luck:

• 𝗙𝗿𝗶𝗮𝘀, 𝗝𝗲𝗻𝗻𝘂𝗲𝗹 𝗛𝗲𝗿𝗯𝗲𝗿𝘁 𝗕𝗿𝗼𝗱𝗶𝘁𝗵
• 𝗟𝗮𝗷𝗮, 𝗦𝗵𝗮𝘆𝗿𝗮 𝗔𝘆𝗮𝗵 𝗦𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗱𝘀𝗼𝗻𝗴
• 𝗟𝗶𝗿𝗮, 𝗘𝗿𝘄𝗶𝗻 𝗥𝘂𝘇𝗸𝗶𝗻
• 𝗢𝗹𝗼𝗿𝗼𝘀𝗶𝘀𝗶𝗺𝗼, 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝘀 𝗘𝘇𝗲𝗸𝗶𝗲𝗹 𝗧𝗮𝗴𝗹𝗲

Your hard work, dedication, and passion for learning have brought you this far, and we believe you have what it takes to truly excel and make us proud. This is your moment to showcase not just knowledge, but also the spirit of teamwork and perseverance that defines a true MedTech Tamaraw. 

Know that you carry the pride and full support of the entire FEU MT community. Goodluck, quizzers!

#PoweredToBeTimeless
#XIIMTSoc
#FEUMTS

Caption by Peachie Corinne Sulit
Publication Material by Rein Louisse Dela Cruz & JC Sadang
